<br />
BUT, in my opinion on net games that are NOT insanely addictive ( that is addictive but using browsers, heck even if it is Ragnarok online kinda thing) YOU should put in, ' ELITE' players.<br />
<br />
Or basicaly, people who bothered to donate and keep the game alive.<br />
<br />
This might require a bit more programming but I shall leave that to Monseour Mind Warper and his excellent team. NOW shut up about it being too biased. IF some one bothered to properly support the game with REAL cold hard cash that feeds the dev team, THEY SHOULD be given that advantage. After all it is like going to a triathlaton with either, a $2000 carbon fibre bike or a $50 Barbie bike you got form christmas.<br />
<br />
Here's the deal:<br />
Non elite players: EVerything right here right now. hey it's free!<br />
<br />
Elite players: I am giving 2 options for the bonuses. I think they are balanced but you may not think so or maybe a mix between the two but NOTHING overly powerful combos.<br />
<br />
Length: 4 weeks or GAME time. So if set's not up no worries mate. If you wasn't playing, no worries mate ( say you miss one set). It only starts ticking down when you have registered your character and ofcourse your Alias is not dead. If server down. No worries mate. I think this is easily done since AS is already 'tick' based so how many 'ticks' is there in an optimal 4 weeks of game? Then just start deducting.<br />
<br />
Criteria: US$5 - 10 decide. Too little is negligible and too much is taxing<br />
<br />
Noting that money transfer companies charge a bit of a cash when you trasnfer your precious dough the elite status is given when you make the donation at the ORIGINAL value. Right so $10 transfer and Mind Warper and co gets $9.25. Hey you made it to the elite status!<br />
<br />
on the side, if you 'exceed' your donation it gets put into a pool which can become an elite boon again. i.e you donated $17 then the next time you donate $3 you are in the elite again.<br />
<br />
To reward the faithful and the sugar daddies. Once a player donates $30 he gets elite status for an extra 1 elite session. If the patriotic then exceeds this $30 and go forth another $30 he gets for the second bonus: 1.75 elite sessions. Not sure if AS is gonna be lasting fopr so long so I am not putting the 'if he gets it the third time' not because the game might die out but because Mind Warper and CO also has other things to do in their life like raising kids and making love.<br />
<br />
Option 1:<br />
Racial bonuses while 'elite' <br />
+ 2 diplomacy.<br />
+ 1 env<br />
+ 1 growth<br />
+ 1 rese<br />
+ 1 prod<br />
+ 1 mil<br />
+ 2 spy<br />
+ 2 comm<br />
+ 1 eff<br />
+ 1 gen<br />
+ 1 FC<br />
<br />
Option 2:<br />
Explore time ALWAYS 2 hours.<br />
+ 4 diplomacy<br />
+ 2 prod<br />
+ 1 rese<br />
+ 1 honour / 6 hours.<br />
<br />
Common bonuses:<br />
Fleets return faster.<br />
<br />
Able to field 2 more fleets in battle. ( max fleet/battle is 20 right?)<br />
<br />
Ability to see diplomatic status of council in the council speaker option IF NOT speaker.<br />
<br />
Ability to customize the archspace browser with pre designed ( by the dev team ofcourse)<br />
<br />
Ability, if Speaker to msg all council members at once( some players are too lazy to read the council forum).<br />
<br />
Ability if speaker, to delete posts in council. ( minimal moderator power)<br />
<br />
Ability if speaker, to DISMISS any one he deems inactive at any time from his council.<br />
<br />
Your name is written in some other colour OR have stars on it depicting your elite stats. OR UBER STARS depicting overly chivalric players who gave $30. The enemy knows who you are, but HEY! You got the goods, why not flaunt it?			   <P align=right></P>
